 travel agent</a></li><li class="w-full pt-20"><a class="font-polysans text-20 leading-110 text-black hover:shadow-underline-blurple dark:text-white dark:hover:shadow-underline-franklin" href="/24065447/self-driving-car-autonomous-tesla-gm-baidu">Dude, where’s my self-driving car?</a></li><li class="w-full pt-20"><a class="font-polysans text-20 leading-110 text-black hover:shadow-underline-blurple dark:text-white dark:hover:shadow-underline-franklin" href="/2024/2/13/24067991/watermark-generative-ai-deepfake-copyright">Watermarking the future</a></li><li class="w-full pt-20"><a class="font-polysans text-20 leading-110 text-black hover:shadow-underline-blurple dark:text-white dark:hover:shadow-underline-franklin" href="/24067997/robots-txt-ai-text-file-web-crawlers-spiders">The text file that runs the internet</a></li><li class="w-full pt-20"><a class="font-polysans text-20 leading-110 text-black hover:shadow-underline-blurple dark:text-white dark:hover:shadow-underline-franklin" href="/24066641/disability-ableism-ai-census-qalys">Automating ableism</a></li><li class="w-full pt-20"><a class="font-polysans text-20 leading-110 text-black hover:shadow-underline-blurple dark:text-white dark:hover:shadow-underline-franklin" href="/24068716/ai-historians-academia-llm-chatgpt">How AI can make history</a></li></ul></div><div class="mb-60 flex flex-col px-20 w-full md:w-1/2"><h3 class="font-manuka text-45 leading-80 tracking-2 text-black dark:text-white">In the News</h3><ul class="mt-12 flex w-full list-disc flex-col space-y-20 divide-y divide-gray-cc border-t border-t-blurple pl-20 marker:text-blurple/100 dark:divide-gray-31 dark:border-t-franklin dark:marker:text-franklin/100"><li class="w-full pt-20"><a class="font-polysans text-20 leading-110 text-black hover:shadow-underline-blurple dark:text-white dark:hover:shadow-underline-franklin" href="/2024/2/15/24074151/openai-sora-text-to-video-ai">OpenAI introduces Sora, its text-to-video AI model</a></li><li class="w-full pt-2